    <title>Combined summary - A Small Modification to Segwit</title>
    <updated>2025-11-12T13:12:39.103689+00:00</updated>
    <link href="https://gnusha.org/url/https://lists.linuxfoundation.org/pipermail/bitcoin-dev/2017-April/014076.html" rel="alternate"/>
